OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a few light showers around this
OL,7,Fevening, and the first half of the
OL,8,Fnight will be mainly dry.
OL,9,
OL,10,CWednesday:FA dull wet start.
OL,11,FBrightening somewhat during the
OL,12,Fmorning but further heavy showers soon
OL,13,Fpushing in.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,16,FUnsettled and rather changeable
OL,17,Fthrough this period with showers or
OL,18,Flonger spells of rain. Often rather
OL,19,Fbreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
